About the job
Please find below the job description

Location - Bangalore

Desired Experience Range : 3 - 5Years

Highest qualification: BE/Btech/MCA/Msc/Bsc (full time)

Desired Competencies (Technical/Behavioral Competency) :

1. Hands-on experience in widely used AI and ML frameworks such as TensorFlow, MLFlow, Kubeflow, Keras, Scikit-learn, Python ML;
2. Has hands-on experience in deep learning, machine learning and mathematical modeling skills;
3. Has excellent understanding of ML and deep learning models e.g. classical regression, neural nets, Computer Vision, NLP, association rules, sequence and cluster analysis, etc.

Responsibility of / Expectations from the Role:

1)Develop models using latest AI, ML and Deep Learning frameworks for automation of business processes across different application tracks;
2) Identify opportunities for curation of new or existing data sources, and applying new models to derive progressively improved outcomes;
3) Design and development AI, ML, Deep Learning based proof-of-concepts for automation of Aadhaar business processes;
